# Module Graph

Overview graph collapsed by module path for readability.
~~~mermaid
graph TD
  subgraph G_internal["internal"]
    M1["internal/server"]
    M2["internal/store"]
  end
  subgraph G_py["py"]
    M3["py/api"]
    M4["py/service"]
  end
  subgraph G_root["root"]
    M5["root"]
  end
  subgraph G_web["web"]
    M7["web/handlers"]
    M6["web/server"]
  end
  M1 --> M2
  M3 --> M4
  M5 --> M1
  M6 --> M7
~~~
